name: Baxton_Studio_Georgios_Modern_Contemporary_Greyish_Beige_Fabric_Upholstered_Headboard
reviews: Extremely nice headboard, very happy with it and I thought the price was reasonable. Could of gotten something cheaper, but not as much product and design, this was excellent, very happy with this purchase.
description: Add a touch of romance to the look and feel of your boudoir with the Georgios Upholstered Headboard.  Featuring clean lines, subtle hues and chic, the Georgios headboard will create a handsome aesthetic in your bedroom interior.  Constructed of solid rubberwood frame and plywood, the headboard is built to last.  Soft polyester fabric in greyish beige over the foam filled headboard provides ample comfort for you to lean against. StyleContemporary, ModernMaterialFoam, Polyester, Rubberwood, WoodTypeAdjustable, UpholsteredFinishBeige Finish, Grey FinishAssemblyAssembly RequiredColorBeige, GreyFurniture PatternSolidProduct FeaturesAdjustable Height
